sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant CLI as TodoCLI
    participant S as TodoStore
    U->>CLI: todo add "buy milk"
    CLI->>S: append(item)
    S->>S: save todos.json

flowchart TD
    Start([用户命令]) --> Parse{参数合法?}
    Parse -->|否| ErrCLI[ERR-CLI-001]
    Parse -->|是| Store[TodoStore.save]
    Store --> Write{写入成功?}
    Write -->|否| ErrStore[ERR-STORE-002]
    Write -->|是| Done([完成])
